<section class="page-policies">
  <div class="page-content__inner">

    <p class="page-content__subtitle">Policies</p>
    <h1 class="page-content__title">How We Work</h1>

    <div class="page-content__body page-content__body--legal">

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Shipping</p>
      <p>We ship internationally. Orders are fulfilled within 2–5 business days. Delivery times vary by destination — typically 5–10 business days within Europe, and 10–20 business days elsewhere.</p>
      <p>Shipping costs are calculated at checkout. We currently ship from within the EU. Import duties and taxes for orders outside the EU are the responsibility of the recipient.</p>

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Returns</p>
      <p>We want you to love what you receive. If something isn't right, we accept returns within 30 days of delivery — unworn, unwashed, with original tags attached.</p>
      <p>To start a return, email us at <a class="page-content__email-link" href="mailto:info@hyperreallove.com">info@hyperreallove.com</a> with your order number and reason. We'll guide you through the next steps.</p>
      <p>Return shipping costs are covered by the customer unless the item is defective or we made an error.</p>

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Exchanges</p>
      <p>We don't offer direct exchanges. If you'd like a different item, return your original order for a refund and place a new order.</p>

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Refunds</p>
      <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we'll process your refund within 5–7 business days to your original payment method. You'll receive an email confirmation when it's done.</p>

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Damaged or Incorrect Items</p>
      <p>If your order arrives damaged or incorrect, please contact us within 7 days of receiving it at <a class="page-content__email-link" href="mailto:info@hyperreallove.com">info@hyperreallove.com</a>. We'll make it right.</p>

      <p class="page-content__section-label">Questions</p>
      <p>For anything not covered here, reach out at <a class="page-content__email-link" href="mailto:info@hyperreallove.com">info@hyperreallove.com</a>. We try to respond within 2 business days.</p>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

